Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gustave Marlowe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that the man from last night\Nis an internationally-wanted criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a member of the group\Nbehind Jade Dusk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a terrorist plot carried out in Asterisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he's a terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have joined Jade Dusk\Nfor monetary reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, there was nothing political\Nabout his motives last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It did sound like he was\Ncarrying out someone's request,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe a big organization's\Nbehind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, why would anyone\Nmake such a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police want to put you under protection.\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like none of us\Nwill be needing protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I have some research to do,\Nso please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all, then we'll be leaving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one second, Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you and Amagiri stay a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you yesterday there was\Nsomething I wanted to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.71,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lonely Strega
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are two things, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind marrying Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Brother?!\NWhat kind of a sick joke is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about if you started out\Nby getting engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have\Nthe wrong idea about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis and I don't have\Nthat kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure, I've heard\Nall about your relationship from Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under these circumstances,\Nit's not that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying this for your sake, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you're going to end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act now,\NJulis will end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is, married off to someone convenient\Nfor the Integrated Enterprise Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you should at least pick someone\Nyou get along with now, while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't dislike Amagiri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Needless to say,\NI don't dislike him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forced that\Nvictory parade on us yesterday so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I thought I should\Nintroduce you two in a casual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But why all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I've always\Nturned you down for such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The situation's changed now, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've won the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, the Integrated Enterprise\NFoundation wasn't all that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to your recent victory,\Nyour value has skyrocketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we can still strike first now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can top his status\Nas your partner in the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you say, Amagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small nation, but I'm sure\Nyou can live quite comfortably here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a bad proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, there would\Nalways be certain strings attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you live in this world,\Nyou can never expect complete freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have no choice but to accept\Nsome kind of constraint or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to choose what kind\Nof constraints you're going to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Julis came to Asterisk\Nto break those constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow myself\Nto be the shackles that bind Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're more serious than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget we ever spoke of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if, for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it turns out that Julis herself\Ndesires such shackles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will you accept her wishes then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Brother, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I can't say\Nuntil it actually happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So there's a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all, please excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say there were two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something stupid again,\NI won't let you get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,would you mind not competing\Nin the Gryps Festa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being serious, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I'm totally serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it during the victory parade,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now your popularity\Nis mind-blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you reach even greater heights,\Nyou could drive me into irrelevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I'd like you\Nto stay out of the Gryps Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totally serious, that was me\Nbegging with all of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the throne in this kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm obedient\Nto the Integrated Enterprise Foundation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm a good-for-nothing\Nwith no interest in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Julis were to win the Gryps Festa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up wielding\Nmore influence than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I wouldn't put it past them\Nto put Julis on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then she would try to change\Nthis country to help the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this country is controlled\Nby the Integrated Enterprise Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis would only end up suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can find\Na way to persuade Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have to be an even bigger\Ngood-for-nothing than I already am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find Julis at the orphanage\Nacross the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she was a child, she's always\Ngone there whenever she was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm leaving her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please do it as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'll let you know\Nas soon as I find out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me from any direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ayato Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're right!\N- Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got here faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did my brother tell you where I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Therese...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Ayato Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Therese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of this church\Nand the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the Phoenix Festa. Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pretty cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.11,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that kid\Nwho used to snivel 24/7?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- There she is!\N- There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time really flies, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our little Julis grew up into a fine\Nyoung princess in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know about princesses\Nwho end up winning the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Julis chose a person like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, never mind that.\NIs that her partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.59,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.26,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to tell us all about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just by the way\Nyou looked at Julis now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.06,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, there's nothing to tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on back to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- See you, Julis!\N- See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask her again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know we caused you a lot of trouble\Nover that incident with Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it actually wasn't me\Nwho saved Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just go ahead and accept her thanks\Non behalf of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see that there are some Genestella\Nmembers among the sisters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, including myself,\Nthere are four of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me, Sister Therese\Nis my Strega mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still teach self-defense to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a greenhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the favorite spot of one of the girls\Nwho used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't like fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and she was a truly kind-hearted girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, sorry! Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it's still too soon for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be rather unstable today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jolbert seemed really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That my brother cares for me\Nmore than anyone else in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and how blessed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why I can't accept\Nthis country's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're doing\Nthe best that you can, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That orphanage has nothing\Nto worry about anymore, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that by winning\Nthe Phoenix Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've attained my goal\Nof rescuing that orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a drop in the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the system this world is built on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just keeps churning out\Nmore and more slums like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Places like that orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And children who have no choice\Nbut to cling to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to free this country,\Nat least, of that curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your wish\Nfor the next Gryps Festa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:12:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that\Nall of a sudden? Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the ground rotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Ophélia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia? Surely you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's it been, about a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did I warn you\Nnot to concern yourself with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My business with you\Nis the same as it was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Ophélia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the world you belong in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only following my own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the power\Nto reverse my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't buy that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, my destiny is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on making me\Ndo as you say, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think it's going to end\Nthe way it did a year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hold up, Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, don't you lift a finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is between me and Ophélia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure,\NI'm going to smash that school badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Livingstone Daisy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's that power\Nof Ophélia Landlufen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, you're in over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anemone Coronaria!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ophélia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's not actually...\Nblocking it with just her Prana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your destiny is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn... to... dust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis! Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the miasma of Erenshkigal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Ayato Amagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've already won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's very sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but even I can't stop the wheels\Nof fate once they start turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to get dragged into this,\Nyou should leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that's just not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Repulsing Crow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Ser=Versta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, I feel like I have\Nzero chance of beating you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasteless, odorless, colorless,\Ntransparent miasma, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pretty mind-blowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be out of your misery soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'd be so kind\Nas to hold off a bit, young miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I've been hired\Nto take out those two myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I get paid on a per head basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, could you\Npossibly let me have that prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Ophélia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where the hell\Nhave you been fooling around?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which part of "don't leave the lab"\Ndon't you get?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I have to say\Nthat was bone-chilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard stories about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I never thought\Nshe was a monster of that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, why don't I take care\Nof my own business, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are my creations,\NOrthrus and Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they as imposing\Nas their legends describe them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style, First Sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fugaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's our Phoenix Festa champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This... I can't evade!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close shave, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is quite a dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew I'd be thwarted like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do,\NGustave Marlowe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind\Ntaking you on now myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not what you want, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you're an annoyingly\Nsmart young lady, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is a golden opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to push it\Nand shall now withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:26.86,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, woe is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:29.61,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These previews\Nthat you've all enjoyed until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.53,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've now reached the very last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.91,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However! Please don't be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 24\NReunion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:37.66,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the next episode, the one true heroine\Nwill finally be left standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.08,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the victor will of course be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.04,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,me!
